text: Is data on your chamber of parliament missing? Complete a survey to add data. If you are interested in a specific issue, complete surveys on plenary, committees, MPs, parliamentary administration, accessibility, ethics, or citizen participation. The full survey, which is linked below, covers all issue areas.
Is some of the data inaccurate? Suggest edits, additions, or changes to the data.
What are parliaments in your country or region doing to expand legislative openness? Add good practices to a growing, global collection of examples.
